Ext.data.JsonP['Titanium_Samples']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Titanium Samples</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-30083144\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Titanium Samples</h1>\n    <p>Studio includes a number of samples with the product. Below is a brief overview of the samples available.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-Chapters\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Chapters</span></h2>\n    <p>    </p>\n<ul class=\"toc-indentation \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Titanium_Samples-section-src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-ImportingaSample\">Importing a Sample</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Titanium_Samples-section-src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-KitchenSink\">Kitchen Sink</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Titanium_Samples-section-src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-Geolocation\">Geolocation</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Titanium_Samples-section-src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-RSSReader\">RSS Reader</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Titanium_Samples-section-src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-TodoList\">Todo List</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-ImportingaSample\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Importing a Sample</span></h2>\n    <p>You can import any of these samples from the Studio Dashboard or from the Samples view.    </p>\n    <p>To import a sample from the dashboard:    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>If the Dashboard isn&apos;t open, click <strong class=\" \">Help</strong> &gt;<strong class=\" \"> Studio</strong> &gt; <strong class=\" \">Show Studio Dashboard</strong>.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Click on the <strong class=\" \">Develop</strong> tab on the dashboard.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Find the sample you want to import and click the <strong class=\" \">Import</strong> button.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Follow the wizard prompts to finish importing the project.    </p>\n</li></ol>    <p>To import a sample from the Samples view:    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>If the Samples view isn&apos;t open, click <strong class=\" \">Window</strong> &gt; <strong class=\" \">Show View</strong> &gt; <strong class=\" \">Samples</strong>.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Right-click on a project and click <strong class=\" \">Import sample as project</strong>, or select a project and click the import button (    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/30083144/import_button.png\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/30083144/import_button.png\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\">\n).    </img></p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Follow the wizard prompts to finish importing the project.    </p>\n</li></ol>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-KitchenSink\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Kitchen Sink</span></h2>\n    <p>The Kitchen Sink samples are demonstrations of the feature set for Titanium Mobile. While examples of what the platform can do, they are not meant to be used as a starting point for application development. However, you can check out <strong class=\" \">Commands &gt; Titanium Mobile</strong> to find a suite of snippets designed to extract the most useful pieces from the Kitchen Sink projects for use in your own applications.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-Geolocation\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Geolocation</span></h2>\n    <p>This is a Titanium sample app that uses native maps to plot locations. With it you can forward geocode addresses and add them as annotations to the map.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-TopicsCovered\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Topics Covered</span></h3>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Using native maps with Titanium.Map    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Adding annotations to native maps    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Remote Data access via Titanium.Network.HTTPClient    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Modular Javascript with CommonJS    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Cross-platform design    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Documentation Links    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p><strong class=\" \">Git repo:</strong> <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://github.com/appcelerator-developer-relations/Sample.Mapping\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/appcelerator-developer-relations/Sample.Mapping</a>    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-Screenshots\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Screenshots</span></h3>\n    <div class=\"tablewrap\">\n        <table class=\"confluenceTable\">\n        <thead class=\" \">    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTh\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/30083144/geolocation.jpg\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/30083144/geolocation.jpg\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\">\n        </img></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n</thead><tfoot class=\" \"/><tbody class=\" \"/>        </table>\n            </div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-RSSReader\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>RSS Reader</span></h2>\n    <p>This is a Titanium Mobile sample app that creates a RSS reader. With it you can pull live RSS feeds from the internet, list them along with thumbnails, then drill down to the article itself.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-TopicsCovered.1\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Topics Covered</span></h3>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Remote Data acccess via Titanium.Network.HTTPClient    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Modular Javascript with CommonJS    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Multiple window app using a single execution context    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Loose coupling of UI and data code using application level events via Ti.App    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Native UI features    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Android menus    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>iOS navigation bar buttons    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>iOS Navigation Controller via Titanium.UI.iPhone.NavigationGroup    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p>Webviews for displaying web content    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Cross-platform design    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p><strong class=\" \">Git repo:</strong> <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://github.com/appcelerator-developer-relations/Sample.RSS\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/appcelerator-developer-relations/Sample.RSS</a>    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-Screenshots.1\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Screenshots</span></h3>\n    <p><strong class=\" \">Phones:</strong>    </p>\n    <div class=\"tablewrap\">\n        <table class=\"confluenceTable\">\n        <thead class=\" \"/><tfoot class=\" \"/><tbody class=\" \">    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTh\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/30083144/rss.jpg\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/30083144/rss.jpg\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\">\n        </img></p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/30083144/rss_iphone.jpg\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/30083144/rss_iphone.jpg\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\">\n        </img></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n</tbody>        </table>\n            </div>\n    <p><strong class=\" \">Tablets:</strong><br>    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/30083144/rss_tablet.jpg\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/30083144/rss_tablet.jpg\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\">\n        </img></br></p>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-TodoList\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Todo List</span></h2>\n    <p>This is a Titanium Mobile sample app that creates a basic todo list. With this app you can maintain a listing of tasks to be completed, add to that list, and mark tasks as done.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-TopicsCovered.2\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Topics Covered</span></h3>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Local storage with SQLite via Titanium.Database    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Modular Javascript with CommonJS    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Multiple window app using a single execution context    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Native UI features    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Android menus    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>iOS navigation bar buttons    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Cross-platform design    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p><strong class=\" \">Git repo:</strong> <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://github.com/appcelerator-developer-relations/Sample.Todo\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/appcelerator-developer-relations/Sample.Todo</a>    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-30083144_TitaniumSamples-Screenshots.2\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Screenshots</span></h3>\n    <div class=\"tablewrap\">\n        <table class=\"confluenceTable\">\n        <thead class=\" \"/><tfoot class=\" \"/><tbody class=\" \">    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTh\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/30083144/todo_master.jpg\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/30083144/todo_master.jpg\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\">\n        </img></p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/30083144/todo_detail.jpg\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/30083144/todo_detail.jpg\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\">\n        </img></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n</tbody>        </table>\n            </div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=30083144\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Titanium Samples"});